---
import { getBrand, internalPath, siteConfig } from "../../site-config";

const termsHref = internalPath("terms-of-service");

function hostnameForBrand(astroHost: string): string {
  if (astroHost) return astroHost;
  try {
    return new URL(siteConfig.canonicalOrigin).hostname;
  } catch {
    return "";
  }
}

const brand = getBrand(hostnameForBrand(Astro.url.hostname));
const phone = siteConfig.phoneDisplay;
const tel = siteConfig.phoneE164;
---

<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="legal-updated"><strong>Last updated:</strong> May 30, 2026</p>

<div class="legal-disclaimer-box">
  <strong>Informational use only</strong>
  This website provides educational context and intake coordination. It is not an engineering report,
  licensed contractor estimate, insurance determination, or appraisal. See our{" "}
  <a href={termsHref}>Terms of Service</a> for full disclaimers.
</div>

<p>
  <strong>Operator:</strong> {brand.name}<br />
  <strong>Website:</strong> {siteConfig.canonicalOrigin}<br />
  <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href={`tel:${tel.replace(/^\+/, "")}`}>{phone}</a>
</p>

<h2>1. Overview</h2>
<p>
  This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you visit our website or
  contact us by phone to request coordination for home services (including roofing, plumbing, pest control,
  water damage, siding, and related residential intake).
</p>
<p>
  We operate a <strong>dispatch and referral network</strong>. We are not the on-site contractor on every
  job. Licensed service providers in your area may perform work under separate agreements.
</p>

<h2>2. Information we collect</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Phone number and call metadata when you use click-to-call or dial our numbers</li>
  <li>Call recordings where permitted by law and disclosed on the call path</li>
  <li>Technical data: IP address, browser type, device, pages visited, referring URL</li>
  <li>Cookies and analytics used to measure site performance (page views, call-button clicks)</li>
  <li>Information you provide during intake (service type, ZIP code, urgency, notes)</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. How we use information</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Route your request to appropriate local responders or partners</li>
  <li>Operate call tracking, routing, and quality assurance (including third-party telephony platforms)</li>
  <li>Improve website content and scheduling workflows</li>
  <li>Comply with legal obligations and respond to lawful requests</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. How we share information</h2>
<p>We may share information with:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Independent contractors or service partners who may contact you about scope and scheduling</li>
  <li>Call tracking, routing, and analytics providers</li>
  <li>Service providers that host or secure our website</li>
  <li>Authorities when required by law</li>
</ul>
<p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell personal information for unrelated third-party marketing.</p>

<h2>5. Illustrative data on service-area pages</h2>
<p>
  Some pages display market anchors, stress or risk indexes, charts, USGS-style terrain references, or
  calculator outputs. These are <strong>illustrative and educational</strong> only. They are not
  professional engineering advice, insurer findings, or guaranteed pricing.
</p>

<h2>6. Your choices</h2>
<p>
  You may decline to provide information, but we may be unable to coordinate service. Cookie controls may
  be available through your browser settings. For privacy questions, call{" "}
  <a href={`tel:${tel.replace(/^\+/, "")}`}>{phone}</a>.
</p>

<h2>7. Data retention</h2>
<p>
  We retain information as needed for dispatch records, billing reconciliation, fraud prevention, and legal
  compliance, then delete or de-identify where appropriate.
</p>

<h2>8. Security</h2>
<p>
  We use reasonable administrative and technical safeguards. No method of transmission over the Internet is
  100% secure.
</p>

<h2>9. Children</h2>
<p>
  Our services are directed to adults requesting property-related help. We do not knowingly collect
  information from children under 13.
</p>

<h2>10. Changes</h2>
<p>We may update this policy. The &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date will change when we do.</p>

<h2>11. Contact</h2>
<p>
  {brand.name}<br />
  Phone: <a href={`tel:${tel.replace(/^\+/, "")}`}>{phone}</a>
</p>
